data.description: Seller contribution of $3000 towards Buyer's closing costs. Buyer financing fell through. Back to the market. Inspections are already done, all good! This Beautiful very well-maintained house is almost 1,800 sq ft, which is plenty of space! Features upgraded bathrooms, a spacious master bedroom (13x22) with a walk-in closet, bonus space for an office or family room, tile flooring, new stucco, recently painted, a new fence installed just 1 year ago, patio and driveway paved, irrigation system connected from a well so save money on water bill, two-car garage. Sits on a large corner lot beautifully landscaped and several fruit trees planted, bring your boat, RV, and toys as is not HOA or deed restricted, either CDD. Located in the heart of Bradenton close to everything, and just 15 minutes from the beach! Come to see it! Make it yours! Send your offer!
